The paper deals with the problem of label shift adaptation in machine learning, which is a common issue in various subfields of computer science such as natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed method involves using EM algorithm and calibration techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.AI, followed by cs.CV, cs.CL, and cs.CR.
